com.dpsframework.util

Class PsGenerate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dpsframework.util.PsGenerate

  • public class PsGenerate
extends java.lang.Object
    Genetare-Tool makes new agents directory-structure on /nodes/ directory. 
     For help, type: 
 
  $ >_  java generate 

  Usage   : java generate [Options]
  Options : [-h  ]                         View extended info.
            [--new=]   Node-name           Make new empty node space.
            [--type=monitor|node|board]    Type of PsAgent.
  
  Examples: java generate --new=PrivatePanel7A   --type=board
            java generate --new=Bot501,Bot521,Bot541,Bot581  --type=engine
            java generate --new=h200  --type=monitor
    Since:
    2018-08-20
    Version:
    1.7 (Build.1814)
    Author:
    Francisco J. Aguayo (Leon University / IEEE Power & Energy Systems Society Member)
    See Also:
    PsLauncher
